OL,7,FA reveller left a Stoke clubber
OL,8,Funconscious - 63 days before he killed
OL,9,Fa drinker with a single punch.
OL,11,FBenjamin Wallbanks floored David Regan
OL,12,Fwith a single punch, in Hanley, on 26
OL,13,FSeptember 2021.
OL,15,FWeeks later he then knocked out Ben
OL,16,FGrosvenor on nearby Trinity Street.
OL,17,FBen, from Burslem, spent two years in
OL,18,Fa coma before losing his fight for
OL,19,Flife.
