OL,7,FWallbanks, of Opal Road, Fenton, was
OL,8,Fsentenced at Stafford Crown Court for
OL,9,FBen's manslaughter. He was also
OL,10,Fsentenced for the attack on Mr Regan.
OL,12,FThe court heard how Mr Regan had gone
OL,13,Fto Hanley after drinking in Burslem
OL,14,Fand had been turned away by bouncers
OL,15,Fat a club.
OL,17,FA dispute broke out in the queue after
OL,18,FWallbanks believed someone had
OL,19,Fthreatened or grabbed his 13-year-old
OL,20,Fson.
