OL,7,FRebecca Wade KC, prosecuting, told the
OL,8,Fcourt: "The defendant was intent on a
OL,9,Fconfrontation with Mr Regan.
OL,11,F"A number of people intervened to try
OL,12,Fto prevent the confrontation taking
OL,13,Fplace. But the defendant pushed and
OL,14,Fmoved towards Mr Regan.
OL,16,F"He broke free and offered a blow with
OL,17,Fhis left hand. It was a jab-style
OL,18,Fpunch to the jaw which caused him
OL,19,Fimmediately to fall to the floor. He
OL,20,Fwas rendered unconscious."
