OL,7,FMr Regan was taken to hospital.
OL,8,FWallbanks was seen to get in a van and
OL,9,Fdrive away.
OL,11,FWallbanks was handed a nine-year
OL,12,Fextended sentence. It includes a six-
OL,13,Fyear prison sentence for the
OL,14,Fmanslaughter and a six-month
OL,15,Fconcurrent prison term for the attack
OL,16,Fon Mr Regan.
